data.description: Situated on a large level corner lot within walking distance to the lake, this well-maintained 3-bedroom home in a highly desired Lake Latonka subdivision features spacious rooms, a formal dining room and two full baths. Fully equipped eat-in kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ceramic tile floors. En suite bath in the mater bedroom and double closets. The finished lower level has a beautiful stone fireplace in the family room, laundry room, and plenty of room for storage.  Over-sized two-car garage, spacious rear deck, and a partially fenced-in yard. This home is truly an EXCEPTIONAL FIND and a MUST-SEE!
